page.title: 05A Pimperne Family.
page.content: My name is Jamie Drennan, I have one younger sister. I am nine. My Dad is a policeman in Blandford.My Mum is a receptionist in the new Blandford hospital.We have a car,a Cavalier.We have a house with a big garden.I live at 8,Parr Grove. I like shepherds pie,so does my sister.My Dad likes chilli con carne, my Mum likes salads. I used to have a cat called Bubbles. We always go to Cornwall on holiday,last year we were on the beach every day. When I get home from school I get my ghostbuster top on and my A team tracksuit.I like watching television.I have got a snooker table and lots more games. My hobby is nature study.
